{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Welcome to Slug Wars by Hovi production!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Prepare for an epic battle down on the seabed. Challenge your friends and slide to victory in <strong>Slug Wars</strong>, our  online multiplayer game! Dominate the ocean floor and prove who's the ultimate Slug champion! <strong>Slug Wars</strong> is an online multiplayer 3rd-person shooter, where you play as cute Sea Slugs, and after being eliminated you get to choose a power up!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445050/extras/SlugFight.gif?t=1738938732\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Slug Wars is made to be played with a group of friends</strong>, and it provides intense and whacky gameplay! If shooter games are not your strongest suit, no worries. In <strong>Slug Wars</strong> even if you get defeated, take yourself a power up, and slide back into action stronger than before!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445050/extras/SlugDance.gif?t=1738938732\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Key mechanic: Power ups!</u></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Slug Wars</strong> features an expanding selection of whacky and fun power ups, that help you in the midst of battle. After getting eliminated, you the player, are presented with three randomly picked power ups to choose from. So choose wisely, since there are no re-takes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445050/extras/PowerUpSelect.gif?t=1738938732\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Character customization!</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Express yourself on the seabed.\u00a0<strong>Slug Wars</strong> features a character customization system, where you get to create yo